several years ago about poems songs in rhyme very good ones came to me i wrote them down fast why has this ever happened to any of you do you know what was going on they came over me like waves i just would grab a pen and write it down i didn't hear it outloud more like loud thoughts a psychic said it was spirits someone else said a muse someone else said the holy spirit i still don't know who it was or why it happened has it happened to any of you please tell me about it if it did thanks spirit muse holy spirit it may have been all of those many times when your mind is in the right place spirits can talk to you or through you it has never happened to me but it has with my best friends mom she can sit on her bed with a pen and paper and if she clears her mind long enough she'll just start writing pages and pages only she didnt write it spirits did through her dont be scared it may be that you have a evry special gift RuneScape quests Time Out of Mind The Shining (film) Jon Secada Holy Spirit Episodes of Lost (Season 1) Milton H. Erickson Similarities between the Bible and the Qur'an Cigarette Smoking Man John Berryman Robert Burns Yu-Gi-Oh! anime and manga characters The Dunciad The SpongeBob SquarePants Movie Sydney Riot of 1879 YuYu Hakusho She Loves You Rapping Jean Grey Eternal Sunshine of the Spotless Mind Pok__mon Live! Blonde on Blonde Boom Crash Opera The Lovely Bones The nature of God in Western theology Xiaolin Showdown Alan Campbell (pastor) Out-of-body experience The Long Game I Want to Hold Your Hand The Star Wars Holiday Special Sri Aurobindo Scarlet's Walk Socrates Book of Mormon The Empty Child Dean Koontz Kristin Hersh A Course In Miracles About a Boy Aquemini H.D. Love and Theft Ron and Fez Ten Commandments Yoga Sutras of Patanjali Ira Gershwin The Marshall Mathers LP Another Side of Bob Dylan John Cage Teen Girl Squad Humphrey Bogart Calvin and Hobbes Highway 61 Revisited Jennifer Lopez Timeline of alternative rock Avenue Q Thomas Fuller Emotions 